org.agilewiki.jactor2.core.reactors

Class BlockingReactor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.agilewiki.jactor2.core.blades.BladeBase
      • org.agilewiki.jactor2.core.reactors.ReactorBase
        • org.agilewiki.jactor2.core.reactors.BlockingReactor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, Blade, BlockingBlade, Closeable, CommonReactor, Reactor

    @GwtIncompatible
public class BlockingReactor
extends ReactorBase
implements CommonReactor, BlockingBlade
    Process requests/responses which may block the thread or tie it up with a long computation.

    Requests/responses are processed one at a time in the order received, except that requests/responses from the same reactor are given preference.

    Requests/responses destined to a different reactor are held until processing is complete for each incoming request/response.
